    {
      "key": "contribution.{E34523C0-5447-11D8-968B-444553540003-titech-mlrv1000}.description",
      "source": "加越能鉄道を引き継いだ第三セクター万葉線のMLRV1000形は2003年12月に登場した超低床電車です。\n\t\t\t基本的な部分は岡山電軌のMOMOと共通ですが、真っ赤な車体が印象的です。\n\t\t\tちなみにデザインは工業デザイナーの佐藤康三氏によるものです。",
      "translation": "The Manyo Line MLRV1000 Series, a third-sector railway that succeeded the Kaetsuno Railway, is an ultra-low-floor tram that appeared in December 2003. Its basic components are shared with Okayama Electric Tramway's MOMO, but its bright red body is striking. The design is by industrial designer Kozo Sato."
    },
